<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Not Safe Here | Website Mockup</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --black: #080706;
      --brown: #2b2118;
      --deep-brown: #4a2e2a;
      --cream: #f5e9e2;
      --soft-cream: #fbf6ef;
      --gold: #c8a96a;
      --dark-gold: #a9823f;
      --text: #191512;
      --muted: #6f6258;
      --border: #ded0c1;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #f7f1ea;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 1440px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--soft-cream);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    header {
      height: 64px;
      background: var(--black);
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 86px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      position: relative;
    }

    .logo::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -12px;
      width: 58px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--gold);
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 42px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-button,
    .gold-button {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), #d8b76f);
      color: #140f0a;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-button {
      text-transform: none;
      letter-spacing: 0;
      padding: 10px 24px;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 360px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.95) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.78) 38%, rgba(0,0,0,0.28) 68%, rgba(0,0,0,0.05) 100%),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
      padding: 78px 86px 65px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 74px;
      line-height: 0.95;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 620px;
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #f1ebe5;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .info-section {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 38% 62%;
      gap: 40px;
      padding: 34px 86px 38px;
      background: var(--soft-cream);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .why {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      padding-right: 30px;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .flower {
      color: #c9bbaa;
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 76px;
      line-height: 1;
      opacity: 0.8;
      transform: rotate(-12deg);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 16px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .section-title::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -11px;
      width: 42px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--gold);
    }

    .why p {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 15.5px;
    }

    .stories-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .view-all {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .story-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .story-card {
      background: #fbf7ef;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 30px 26px 18px;
      min-height: 180px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }

    .quote-mark {
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      color: var(--dark-gold);
      font-size: 52px;
      line-height: 0.6;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .story-card blockquote {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.35;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .story-card cite {
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .submit-section {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #3b2a1c, var(--black));
      color: white;
      padding: 24px 86px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 28% 40% 32%;
      gap: 32px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .submit-copy {
      padding-right: 26px;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    }

    .submit-copy p {
      color: #f1e9dd;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .privacy-note {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      color: #ddd0c2;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .lock {
      border: 1px solid #ddd0c2;
      border-radius: 4px;
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      margin-top: 3px;
    }

    form {
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      padding-right: 32px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    textarea,
    input {
      width: 100%;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 14px;
      font-family: inherit;
      background: #fbf7ef;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    textarea {
      height: 78px;
      resize: none;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .two-fields {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .checkbox-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .checkbox-row input {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      accent-color: var(--gold);
    }

    .tags {
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .tag-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 11px;
      margin: 18px 0 24px;
    }

    .tag {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .support-box {
      background: #fbf7ef;
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .heart {
      background: #2c2118;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 23px;
    }

    .support-box h3 {
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .support-box p {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: #3e352f;
    }

    footer {
      background: var(--soft-cream);
      padding: 24px 86px 34px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 32% repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }

    footer h2 {
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 27px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    footer h4 {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    footer a,
    footer p {
      display: block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #4a413a;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .socials {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      header,
      .hero,
      .info-section,
      .submit-section,
      footer {
        padding-left: 28px;
        padding-right: 28px;
      }

      nav {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
      }

      .info-section,
      .submit-section,
      footer {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .why,
      .submit-copy,
      form {
        border-right: none;
        padding-right: 0;
      }

      .story-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <div class="logo">Not Safe Here.</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#stories">Stories</a>
        <a href="#submit">Submit</a>
        <a href="#resources">Resources</a>
        <button class="nav-button">Share Your Story</button>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>Campus Safety<br><span>Isn’t Equal.</span></h1>
          <h2>Black women know this firsthand.</h2>
          <p>Not Safe Here is a platform amplifying the anonymous experiences of Black women navigating safety, silence, and survival on college campuses.</p>
          <button class="gold-button">Share Your Story (Anonymously)</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="info-section" id="about">
        <div class="why">
          <div class="flower">✧</div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Why This Exists</h2>
            <p>Universities often claim to prioritize student safety, yet many Black women experience harm that goes unheard, unaddressed, and unacknowledged.</p>
            <p><strong>Not Safe Here</strong> challenges these narratives by creating space for anonymous storytelling that centers lived experience over institutional image.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="stories">
          <div class="stories-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">Featured Stories</h2>
            <a class="view-all" href="#">View all stories →</a>
          </div>

          <div class="story-grid">
            <article class="story-card">
              <div class="quote-mark">“</div>
              <blockquote>I didn’t feel safe walking back to my dorm... but I felt even less safe reporting it.</blockquote>
              <cite>— Anonymous, Sophomore</cite>
            </article>

            <article class="story-card">
              <div class="quote-mark">“</div>
              <blockquote>He was still in my class the next day. Nothing changed—except me.</blockquote>
              <cite>— Anonymous, Senior</cite>
            </article>

            <article class="story-card">
              <div class="quote-mark">“</div>
              <blockquote>I knew reporting it would mean reliving it... and still not being believed.</blockquote>
              <cite>— Anonymous, 21</cite>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="submit-section" id="submit">
        <div class="submit-copy">
          <h2 class="section-title">Share Your Story</h2>
          <p>Your story deserves to be heard—on your terms. You can submit anonymously. No names. No identifying details. Just your truth.</p>

          <div class="privacy-note">
            <div class="lock">✓</div>
            <p>We prioritize your safety and privacy. Submissions are reviewed to remove identifying information before being shared.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <form>
          <label for="story">Your Story</label>
          <textarea id="story" placeholder="Write your story here..."></textarea>

          <div class="two-fields">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Age (optional)">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Year in School (optional)">
          </div>

          <div class="checkbox-row">
            <input type="checkbox" id="share" checked>
            <label for="share">Share my story on the website anonymously</label>
          </div>

          <button type="button" class="gold-button">Submit Story</button>
        </form>

        <div class="tags">
          <h2 class="section-title">Common Experiences</h2>
          <div class="tag-row">
            <span class="tag">#NotBelieved</span>
            <span class="tag">#Reporting</span>
            <span class="tag">#Silence</span>
            <span class="tag">#CampusSafety</span>
            <span class="tag">#Survival</span>
            <span class="tag">#Support</span>
          </div>

          <div class="support-box">
            <div class="heart">♡</div>
            <div>
              <h3>You are not alone.</h3>
              <p>These stories are not isolated. They are part of a larger pattern that deserves to be seen, heard, and addressed.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer id="resources">
      <div>
        <h2>Not Safe Here.</h2>
        <p>Black women’s stories. Our truth. Our power.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4>About</h4>
        <a href="#">Our Mission</a>
        <a href="#">How It Works</a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4>Stories</h4>
        <a href="#">All Stories</a>
        <a href="#">Browse by Theme</a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4>Resources</h4>
        <a href="#">Get Help</a>
        <a href="#">Report & Support</a>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4>Connect</h4>
        <div class="socials">◎ 𝕏 ✉</div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
